AveragePriceMatched

The average price matched at. Voided match fragments are removed from this average calculation. The price is automatically adjusted in the event of non runners being declared with applicable reduction factors. This value is not meaningful for activity on LINE markets and is not guaranteed to be returned or maintained for these markets.

[JsonPropertyName("averagePriceMatched")]
public double AveragePriceMatched { get; init; }
